{"id":47710,"date":"2024-02-25T22:38:50","date_gmt":"2024-02-25T17:08:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=47710"},"modified":"2023-08-05T15:01:45","modified_gmt":"2023-08-05T09:31:45","slug":"balcony-storage-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-storage-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Balcony Storage Ideas to Add Fun &#038; Functionality to Your Outdoor Space"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Discover balcony storage solutions to maximise your outdoor space and keep it organised!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With real estate getting increasingly expensive every passing day, finding apartments or condos with spacious balconies is becoming difficult. You need creative balcony storage solutions to make the most of your space.&nbsp; Whether you&#8217;re looking to store books, display <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/outdoor-furniture-ideas\/\">outdoor furniture<\/a> and plants, or create a functional laundry space &#8211; we&#8217;ve got you covered! So let&#8217;s dive right in.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Balcony Storage Cabinet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The easiest way to maximise your space is through a balcony storage cabinet. Check out this bright yellow storage cabinet with shutters and drawers. Its vibrant colour lends freshness and a feel-good ambience to the outdoor space. You can use the space above the cabinet to display decor items and the insides to keep delicate items like crockery, glasses, wine bottles, etc, safe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145159\/balcony-storage-cabinet.jpg\" alt=\"Balcony storage cabinet with shutters and drawers in yellow colour\" class=\"wp-image-48045\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145159\/balcony-storage-cabinet.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145159\/balcony-storage-cabinet-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145159\/balcony-storage-cabinet-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145159\/balcony-storage-cabinet-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Compact, sleek outdoor storage cabinet for balcony<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Floating Wall Shelves Instead of a Balcony Storage Unit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If a balcony storage cabinet is not enough and you&#8217;re looking to add more storage, these wall-mount shelves are a huge saviour. They can be installed in the smallest spaces and utilised in various ways. As you can see in this image, the wall shelves can be used to stack your favourite books, display your artwork, or hold scented candles and souvenirs from your travels.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145153\/balcony-floating-wall-shelves-for-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Floating wall shelves as a balcony storage solution suitable for smallest spaces\" class=\"wp-image-48044\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145153\/balcony-floating-wall-shelves-for-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145153\/balcony-floating-wall-shelves-for-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145153\/balcony-floating-wall-shelves-for-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145153\/balcony-floating-wall-shelves-for-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Wall shelves to store and display items on the balcony<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Hidden Storage Bench Replace Outdoor Balcony Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The most versatile <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/outdoor-balcony-furniture-design-ideas\/\">balcony furniture<\/a> with storage is a bench. Not only does it offer seating space, but it also offers hidden storage underneath to help keep the area uncluttered. Use it to store cleaning essentials, gardening tools, outdoor cushions, or barbecue accessories. Everything you need will be right at your fingertips, making outdoor activities like gardening or hosting barbeque parties more convenient.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145141\/hidden-balcony-storage-solution.jpg\" alt=\"Hidden balcony storage bench which maximises space\" class=\"wp-image-48042\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145141\/hidden-balcony-storage-solution.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145141\/hidden-balcony-storage-solution-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145141\/hidden-balcony-storage-solution-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145141\/hidden-balcony-storage-solution-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Storage benches maximise space in a compact balcony<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Open Storage For Balcony<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best apartment balcony transformation ideas is to turn it into a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/laundry-room-ideas-in-balcony\/\">laundry space<\/a>. You can create a functional laundry space even on a tiny balcony and free up space inside the house. Check out this compact area with a washing machine and ample open-box shelves to store cleaning supplies. You can use the hanging space and the shelves to hang or stack washed clothes neatly.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145148\/balcony-open-storage-solution.jpg\" alt=\"Open storage for balcony for seamless laundry experience\" class=\"wp-image-48043\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145148\/balcony-open-storage-solution.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145148\/balcony-open-storage-solution-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145148\/balcony-open-storage-solution-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145148\/balcony-open-storage-solution-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Balcony storage for a seamless laundry experience<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Balcony Shoe Rack<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A covered <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/shoe-rack-design-ideas\/\">shoe rack<\/a> is an excellent waterproof balcony storage solution that helps keep your shoes safe and your home tidy. Add a tall, narrow one to the area to fit in a corner or against a wall without taking up too much room. Check out how this mustard shoe rack makes the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/small-balcony-design-ideas\/\">small balcony<\/a> come alive!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145135\/balcony-shoe-storage-rack.jpg\" alt=\"Balcony shoe storage rack for organised and stylish storage\" class=\"wp-image-48041\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145135\/balcony-shoe-storage-rack.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145135\/balcony-shoe-storage-rack-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145135\/balcony-shoe-storage-rack-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145135\/balcony-shoe-storage-rack-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Organised and stylish shoe storage solution<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Space saving balcony spaces for an aesthetic vibe!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/27114809\/space-saving-balcony-spaces-for-an-aesthetic-vibe-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Outdoor Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for an innovative dry balcony storage option? Then this coffee table with bright yellow ottomans is a must-have! It transforms your compact outdoor space into a stylish seating space for four. Push the ottomans under the coffee table when not in use to effortlessly free up floor space. The best part? These ottomans have hidden storage space that helps keep your home neat and well-kept.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145128\/balcony-coffee-table-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Outdoor coffee table with yellow ottomans as balcony storage solution\" class=\"wp-image-48040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145128\/balcony-coffee-table-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145128\/balcony-coffee-table-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145128\/balcony-coffee-table-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145128\/balcony-coffee-table-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Space-saving furniture with high utility is great for outdoors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Plant Organizer For Balcony<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re a plant lover, this plant organiser can be a wonderful addition to your outdoor space. This multi-layer stand maximises the number of plants you can grow in a limited space. It utilises the vertical space to display a variety of plants without sacrificing valuable floor room. Fill it with succulents, flowering plants, creepers and more to create a green corner.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145122\/balcony-multi-plant-organiser-for-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Multi-plant organiser as a balcony storage solution which is tidy and chic\" class=\"wp-image-48039\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145122\/balcony-multi-plant-organiser-for-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145122\/balcony-multi-plant-organiser-for-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145122\/balcony-multi-plant-organiser-for-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/05145122\/balcony-multi-plant-organiser-for-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Keep it tidy and chic with a multi-plant organiser<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, with these outdoor balcony storage ideas, you can maximise your home&#8217;s storage potential and add visual interest to the space. This way, you&#8217;ll be able to enjoy your space to the fullest. And if you need expert help to find <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interior solutions<\/a> that increase storage by 20%, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">reach out to our experienced designers<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Balcony Storage Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How<\/strong> <strong>do I choose the right balcony storage solution for my needs?<\/strong><br>Choosing the right storage solutions depends on the size and layout of your balcony. Consider the items you need to store and how often you will access these items. This will help you decide on the right storage solution. Look for solutions that offer ample storage without taking up too much balcony space and complement the overall look and feel of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How can I maximise storage space on my balcony?<\/strong><br>Invest in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/multifunctional-furniture-designs\/\">multifunctional furniture<\/a> pieces like a bookshelf with a hidden wine cabinet or a bench that offer drawers underneath for storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are the benefits of having balcony storage?<\/strong><br>Balcony storage options allow you to utilise your outdoor space more efficiently and keep your home clutter-free and well-organised. This will make it easier to find the items you need and keep them safe from dust, excessive sunlight, and any damage caused by weather.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are some common balcony storage solutions?<\/strong><br>Storage benches are the most common balcony storage solution. In addition to seating, they offer space to store books, outdoor cushions, board games, and other knickknacks. Wall-mounted shelves and storage cabinets are great options for storing small plants, gardening tools, cleaning supplies, and decor items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I organise my balcony storage to maximise space?<\/strong><br>Utilise your balcony&#8217;s vertical space by installing wall-mounted shelves and cabinets. Invest in a storage bench, a side table, or a bookshelf with built-in storage to maximise space and improve the aesthetics of your balcony.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore more:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-decoration-ideas\/\">Balcony Decoration Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-glass-door-design\/\">Balcony Glass Door Designs<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n             